                     <interp inst="t18020918-77-person588" type="gender" value="male"></interp>
                  </persName>
             and Julia-Ann Robertson were married in this church, by banns, this 31st day of January, 1797.</p>
               <p>Signed, Edward O'Dannel and Julia-
               <persName id="t18020918-77-person589">
                  Ann 
                  Robertson
               <interp inst="t18020918-77-person589" type="surname" value="Robertson"></interp>
